class.name: SchListOfBSTRs
class.abstract: Represents a non-persistant list of character strings to be used with Schematic IDLs.

method.name: Append
method.abstract: Adds a character string to the end of the list.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a character string from its index in the list.

method.name: RemoveByIndex
method.abstract: Remove a character string from the list by specifying its position in the list.

method.name: Count
method.abstract: Returns the number of character strings in the list.

class.name: SchListOfDoubles
class.abstract: Represents a list of DOUBLEs to be used with Schematic IDLs.

method.name: Append
method.abstract: Adds a double to the end of the list.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a double from its index in the list.

method.name: RemoveByIndex
method.abstract: Remove a double from the list by specifying its position in the list.

method.name: Count
method.abstract: Returns the number of doubles in the list.

class.name: SchListOfLongs
class.abstract: Represent a non-persistant list of LONGs to be used with schematic IDLs.

method.name: Append
method.abstract: Adds an long integer to the end of the list.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a long integer from its index in the list.

method.name: RemoveByIndex
method.abstract: Remove a long integer from the list by specifying its position in the list.

method.name: Count
method.abstract: Returns the number of long integers in the list.

class.name: SchListOfObjects
class.abstract: Represent a non-persistant list of schematic objects.

method.name: Append
method.abstract: Adds an object to the end of the list.

method.name: Item

method.name: RemoveByIndex
method.abstract: Remove an object from the list by specifying its position in the list.

method.name: Count
method.abstract: Returns the number of objects in the list.

method.abstract: Query whether it is OK to break.

method.name: OKToConcatenate
method.abstract: Query whether it is OK to concatenate.

method.name: RemovePoints
method.abstract: Remove points from route.

method.name: ReshapeExtremity
method.abstract: Change the position of the extremity of the route.

method.name: SetPath

class.abstract: Manage a symbol placed on a route.

method.abstract: Mirror the symbol over the route segment line on which the symbol is positioned.

method.name: Scale

method.name: SetPosition
